The {{nihongo|Ono family|小野氏}} are the priests of [[Hinomisaki Shrine]]. They descend from {{ill|Ame-no-Fuyukinu|lt=Ame-no-Fuyukinu's|ja|天之冬衣神|1=Ame-no-Fuyukinu|simple|User:Immanuelle/Ame-no-Fuyukinu|en|12=draft}} son {{ill|Kiyotake Toyohiko no Mikoto|ja|清武豊彦命|simple|User:Immanuelle/Kiyotake Toyohiko no Mikoto|12=draft}} brother of [[Ōkuninushi]] and often intermarried with the [[Izumo clan]]. <ref>[[:ja:小野尊光|Takamitsu Ono]]『小野家譜』(Histoire de la famille Ono)（{{ill|Historiographical Institute of the University of Tokyo|en}}, 1875）</ref>
