[[ja:小野氏_(社家)]]
[[en:Ono Family (Shake)]]
[[sn:Ono Family (Shake)]]
[[Category:出雲国の氏族]]
[[Category:小野氏 (社家)]]

The {{nihongo|Ono family|小野氏}} are the priests of [[Hinomisaki Shrine]]. They descend from [[:en:Ame-no-Fuyukinu|Ame-no-Fuyukinu's]] son {{ill|Kiyotake Toyohiko no Mikoto|ja|清武豊彦命|simple|User:Immanuelle/Kiyotake Toyohiko no Mikoto|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kiyotake Toyohiko no Mikoto|qq=}} brother of [[Ōkuninushi]] and often intermarried with the [[Izumo clan]]. <ref>[[:ja:小野尊光|Takamitsu Ono]]『小野家譜』(Histoire de la famille Ono)（{{ill|Historiographical Institute of the University of Tokyo|en|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Historiographical Institute of the University of Tokyo|qq=}}, 1875）</ref>
